# MotoKart rig — hull root, wheels parented to it, pivot at each axle
part hull parent -1 pivot 0 0 0
part trim parent hull pivot 0 0 0
part wheel_fl parent hull pivot -0.245 0.070 0.300
part wheel_fr parent hull pivot 0.245 0.070 0.300
part wheel_rl parent hull pivot -0.260 0.080 -0.260
part wheel_rr parent hull pivot 0.260 0.080 -0.260
